---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Base
  title="About | Paul Koeck"
>
  <div class="prose prose-invert prose-base max-w-none">
    <h1 class="font-semibold">About</h1>

    <p>
      <img
        src="/portrait.jpg"
        alt="Paul Koeck"
        width="448"
        height="448"
        decoding="async"
        fetchpriority="high"
        class="rounded-3xl size-48 object-cover float-left mr-6 mb-2 mt-0 not-prose"
      />
      Hi, I'm Paul. My last name is actually spelled <em>Köck</em>, but since
      almost nobody outside the German-speaking world stands a chance at
      pronouncing that, I go by Koeck online.
    </p>
    <p>
      I'm based in Vorarlberg, the small westernmost corner of Austria wedged
      between Germany, Switzerland, and Liechtenstein.
    </p>
    <p>
      I spend most of my time building software and poking at it to see what
      breaks. On the building side, that spans web, desktop, and mobile, mostly
      in TypeScript these days. On the breaking side, it's web application
      security: finding bugs in software that other people depend on and
      (hopefully) making the internet a slightly less broken place.
    </p>
    <p>
      I run NixOS on everything I can get away with. Yes, that is my biggest
      flex. No, I will not stop talking about it. If you've ever wanted a
      machine you can nuke and rebuild from a single config file, you already
      know why.
    </p>
    <p>
      If any of this resonates, or you've found something interesting you want
      to share, my inbox is open.
    </p>
  </div>


  <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm">
    <a href="https://github.com/paulkoeck" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
      <Icon name="simple-icons:github" class="size-4" />
      GitHub
    </a>
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/paulkoeck" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
      <Icon name="simple-icons:linkedin" class="size-4" />
      LinkedIn
    </a>
    <a href="https://x.com/pauxels" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
      <Icon name="simple-icons:x" class="size-4" />
      X
    </a>
    <a href="https://matrix.to/#/@paul:koeck.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
      <Icon name="simple-icons:matrix" class="size-4" />
      Matrix
    </a>
    <a href="mailto:paul@koeck.dev" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-zinc-800/50 text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">
      <Icon name="lucide:mail" class="size-4" />
      paul@koeck.dev
    </a>
  </div>
</Base>
